  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Cleric Domain</strong><br/><br/><p><b>Deities: </b>Akuma, Damerrich, General Susumu, Gorum, Iomedae, Jaidi, Jaidz, Kols, Myr, Osolmyr, Quindiovatos, Ra, Rubicante, Sarenrae, Shizuru, Skode, Uruskreil, Vonymos</p><p><b>Granted Powers: </b>You are infused with the glory of the divine, and are a true foe of the undead. In addition, when you channel positive energy to harm undead creatures, the save DC to halve the damage is increased by 2.</p><p><b>Domain Spells: </b>1st-shield of faith, 2nd-bless weapon, 3rd-searing light, 4th-holy smite, 5th-righteous might, 6th-undeath to death, 7th-holy sword, 8th-holy aura, 9th-gate.</p>",
